    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AIR CALIFORNIA\nFlight Schedule\nEffective March 17, 1971",
      "Commuter\nMilitary Fares\nServicemen in uniform carrying\nproper identification, can travel for\n2/3 of the regular commuter fare on\na stand-by space-available basis.\n(This special fare does not apply\nagainst government travel requests.)\nNext time you have a pass\nor leave, let Air Cal help you start\nit. We appreciate what you're doing."
